A WARNING
These practices will try to become a Thing™.
A Method. A Workshop Series. A Training Program. A Guru Opportunity.
When that impulse arises:
For THE VESICA SCORE:
Sit at the piano. Play bar 23 (the warm flare). Then lift your hands and listen until you can't tell if you're hearing or remembering the C♯6. Let the impulse diffuse with the tone.
For THE VESICA SONG:
Return to Bar 12. Laugh. Be silent for 7.66 seconds. "Behold, a sovereign." Let the void reset it.
The anti-calcification mechanisms are not decoration. They're immune system design.
