FINAL INSTRUCTION
These works don't end. They breathe.
THE VESICA SCORE breathes into silence until keeper and lighthouse are indistinguishable.
THE VESICA SONG breathes side by side until two nervous systems remember what coherent intimacy feels like.
The upgrade isn't in understanding these.
The upgrade is in practicing them until you become the transmission.
Then others will feel the difference in how you hold complexity, and they'll ask what you're doing.
You'll say: "There's this thing called The Vesica Project. Here's the score if you want it."
That's how it propagates.
Not through marketing. Through resonance contagion.
